{{champion:107}} 
there is no fucking reason this guy should be allowed to 100-0 you from stealth with only a warrior. ive had rengars gank me level 6 miss the bola and the snare an still kill me just off the pure damage his Q does.

like ive seen 1-8 rengars fking kill me like wtf. and the only counterplay is to sit under a pink ward surrounded by your teammates who have korean like reflexes to get cc/exhaust off.  late game this guy is pure cancer he will eliminate anyone who is doing well on your team in an instant.
